Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
getInstPowerDomain(25.10)                            getInstPowerDomain(25.10)

Name
       getInstPowerDomain - Returns the power domain of the instance

Syntax
       getInstPowerDomain

       <instanceName>

       -help

       Returns the power domain of the instance.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes the type and default
              information for getInstPowerDomain.

              For a detailed description of the command and  all  its  parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man getInstPowerDomain

Example
       The following command returns the power domain of the instance:

       getInstPowerDomain a/ff1

       PD1

Related Information
       Low Power Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

